dct_title_s: Southern Morocco 1:125,000. Igherm, sheet 45. A.M.S. P632
dct_description_sm: AMS 1. Alternate title: No. 45 Igherm. Polyconic projection. Northwest Africa and North Sahara zone grids. Relief shown by 82 foot form line intervals. Compiled from Service Geographique du Maroc 1:100,000, 1930 to 1934. Road classifications corrected from Army Map Service road map Northwest Africa, 1:1,000,000, 1942.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
